cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Setting the IPv4 address for NG-AMF to an unreachable network (10.0.0.1) disrupts control plane connectivity, preventing NGAP signaling and gNB registration.

du.explanation_en: Altering the downlink timing advance parameters (T1a_cp_dl) introduces timing inconsistencies, causing synchronization issues and potential frame misalignment in the front-haul interface.
